nodes.text: The Nym Protectorate was a region on the planet Lok. Nym's Stronghold was located in this region.

In the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, the Nym Protectorate was one of many designated planetary regions. The game, developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, was shut down on December 15, 2011.
